{
  "texts": [
    "After its production, the GWB is damped due to quantum interactions with the particles of the primordial plasma at the radiation-dominated epoch, and redshifted inversely proportionally to the scale factor (as it also occurs to radiation) starting from the epoch of matter-radiation equality (Saikawa & Shirai 2018).",
    "The present value of the fractional energy density is then:",
    "g * s (T) g * s (T eq) -4",
    "where T is the temperature of the Universe at the moment when structures of a typical size 1/k re-enter the horizon foot_8, T eq is the temperature of the Universe at the epoch of matter-radiation equality, g * and g * s are relativistic degrees of freedom and degrees of freedom in entropy, respectively.",
    "The final expression for the auto-power spectral density of the timing residuals is:"
  ]
}